<Link id="l00013" /><CodeLine lineNumber="13"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The Simple Packed Serialization (SPS) utilities are used to generate</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00014" /><CodeLine lineNumber="14"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// argument and return buffers for wrapper functions using the following</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00015" /><CodeLine lineNumber="15"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// serialization scheme:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00016" /><CodeLine lineNumber="16"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00017" /><CodeLine lineNumber="17"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Primitives (signed types should be two&#39;s complement):</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00018" /><CodeLine lineNumber="18"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   bool, char, int8&#95;t, uint8&#95;t -- 8-bit (0=false, 1=true)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00019" /><CodeLine lineNumber="19"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   int16&#95;t, uint16&#95;t           -- 16-bit little endian</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00020" /><CodeLine lineNumber="20"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   int32&#95;t, uint32&#95;t           -- 32-bit little endian</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00021" /><CodeLine lineNumber="21"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   int64&#95;t, int64&#95;t            -- 64-bit little endian</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00592" /><CodeLine lineNumber="592"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00593" /><CodeLine lineNumber="593"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Helper type for serializing Errors.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00594" /><CodeLine lineNumber="594"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00595" /><CodeLine lineNumber="595"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// llvm::Errors are move-only, and not inspectable except by consuming them.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00596" /><CodeLine lineNumber="596"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// This makes them unsuitable for direct serialization via</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00597" /><CodeLine lineNumber="597"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// SPSSerializationTraits, which needs to inspect values twice (once to</span></CodeLine>
